Perfection is of two kinds, inchoative or complete, partial or entire.
Complete perfection (the complete digestion of all crudities and elimination
of all impurities) is the ultimate aim of Natureï¼š and she has reached it in
our gold, which with its brilliancy lights up the whole earth.
